{"type":"message","id":"698030da","parentId":"4e570841","timestamp":"2026-04-28T03:30:49.999Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to take note of the currently visible posts BEFORE scrolling, then scroll to get more, note those, and keep going until I have 50 posts total. So I need to:\n\n1. Take a snapshot and record all the posts I see\n2. Scroll down\n3. Take another snapshot and record NEW posts (not ones I've already seen)\n4. Repeat until I have 50\n\nLet me start fresh - refresh the page, get the initial posts, record them with their text/content so I can track which ones are new as I scroll.\n","thinkingSignature":"306ee0ae45e70ccf8cddc1691dd75640eb849d35afdba0ab9597a08411ac4bfd"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_g72m3n8f06b0_1","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"navigate","targetId":"097BA166492C4CA2D14542621CE7B0D3","url":"https://x.com/home"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":6020,"output":183,"cacheRead":74240,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80443,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777347043971,"responseId":"063f5ce42f7f4cc6f76713272aaf2cb4"}}
