{"type":"message","id":"8813dc61","parentId":"1cc80150","timestamp":"2026-04-28T03:39:23.387Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to take note of the posts visible BEFORE scrolling, collect 50 posts total. The issue is X only keeps ~6-10 posts in DOM at any time. Let me try a different approach - I'll scroll and snapshot repeatedly, saving each batch before the next scroll. The key is to save the post content RIGHT AFTER each snapshot, before scrolling again.\n\nLet me start fresh and be systematic about this. I'll scroll → snapshot → save → repeat.","thinkingSignature":"3f45cdf2dd35bdbbbab80f063cf8c71c7b628c227cc4ff57474f4c957c803c58"},{"type":"text","text":"On it. Let me start fresh — I'll scroll, snapshot, save each batch. X only keeps ~6-10 posts in DOM at any time so I need to save immediately after each scroll before the old posts get purged.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_i1lfrj0f345r_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-x/x_for_you_posts.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":146,"output":183,"cacheRead":13925,"cacheWrite":34198,"totalTokens":48452,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777347236085,"responseId":"063f5da474d4e3fa02bf0dfaa50491e5"}}
{"type":"message","id":"10380f66","parentId":"8813dc61","timestamp":"2026-04-28T03:39:23.388Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_i1lfrj0f345r_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# For You Feed Posts - 2026-04-27\n\n## Post 1\n**@JulianGoldieSEO** | 22h ago\nBuild local AI agent with Ollama + Gemma 4 + PI Agent + Parallel Web Search MCP. Free alternative to $20-500/mo agents.\n📊 3.7K views | 81 likes | 132 bookmarks\n\n## Post 2\n**@eclincher** (Ad) | AI Social Media Agent tool - create, schedule, approve posts. $25/mo.\n📊 2.7M views | 181 likes\n\n## Post 3\n**@boxmining** | 18h ago\nOpenClaw 4.24 drops: Google Meet integration, DeepSeek V4 models, Gemini live voice, browser fixes.\n📊 9.2K views | 86 likes\n\n## Post 4\n**@DHSgov** | 3h ago | via @Kimberlyrja8\n\"ICE is NICE.\"\n📊 305K views | 15K likes\n\n## Post 5\n**@AntoineRSX** | 23h ago\nChinese lab open-sourced AI that builds video games from one prompt. Hardest test for coding agents.\n📊 3.5K views | 35 likes\n\n## Post 6\n**@googlegemma** | 10h ago\nCompletely local browser agent powered by Gemma 4 + WebGPU. Searches browsing history, summarizes pages, manages tabs. 100% local, no servers.\n📊 280K views | 4K likes\n\n## Post 7\n**@elonmusk** | 11h ago\n\"Scam Altman and Greg Stockman stole a charity. Full stop.\" - Claims Altman got tens of billions in side deals. 18M views, 120K likes.\n📊 18M views | 120K likes\n\n---\n*Scrolling more...*\n\n## Post 8\n**@plutusmedia** (Ad) | UGC agency marketing - \"one of the most respected operators called us the best UGC agency out there\"\n📊 1.8M views | 239 likes\n\n## Post 9\n**@gregisenberg** | 3h ago\n64-min OpenAI Codex masterclass. Covers: Claude vs Codex, running Claude Code inside Codex, GPT 5.5 for browser agents.\n📊 30K views | 332 likes | 610 bookmarks\n\n## Post 10\n**@sairahul1** | 21h ago\nMicrosoft open-sourced VibeVoice ASR - free 7B model that transcribes 60 mins of audio in one pass. 50+ languages, full diarization, no chunking. Killed ElevenLabs, AssemblyAI, Deepgram pricing.\n📊 830K views | 3K likes | 4.8K bookmarks\n\n## Post 11\n**@NousResearch** | 3h ago\nHermes agent can now run TouchDesigner (powerful real-time visual tool). Video by @macbethAI using the TouchDesigner skill.\n📊 44K views | 876 likes | 638 bookmarks\n\n## Post 12\n**@maverickecom** | 5h ago\nClaude + Arcads = 550 slideshow posts per day. Pro tip: have models hold iPhone over face for more realistic AI look.\n📊 17K views | 170 likes\n\n---\n*Continued scrolling...*"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777347246503}}
