    - button \"Grok actions\" [ref=e41]\n        - button \"More\" [ref=e42]\n        - text: \"Last year I was paying $20/mo for ChatGPT. This year I run my own AI agent for $0. The shift happened when I discovered two open-source tools nobody talks about: → Open WebUI (the chat interface) → Hermes (the self-improving agent) Open WebUI has 130K+ GitHub stars.\"\n        - button \"Show more\" [ref=e43]\n        - text: 8:04\n        - group \"3 replies, 4 reposts, 30 likes, 42 bookmarks, 2149 views\":\n          - button \"3 Replies. Reply\" [ref=e44]: \"3\"\n          - button \"4 reposts. Repost\" [ref=e45]: \"4\"\n          - button \"30 Likes. Like\" [ref=e46]: \"30\"\n          - link \"2149 views. View post analytics\" [ref=e47]:\n            - /url: /JulianGoldieSEO/status/2048722091323879854/analytics\n            - text: 2.1K\n          - button \"Bookmark\" [ref=e48]\n          - button \"Share post\" [ref=e49]\n      - article \"Triserc Verified account @Triserc I typed in a domain and got this Embedded video Play Video From triserc.com 3 reposts, 19 likes, 15 bookmarks, 164855 views\" [ref=e50]:\n        - link \"Triserc Verified account\" [ref=e51]:\n          - /url: /Triserc\n          - text: Triserc\n        - link \"@Triserc\" [ref=e52]:\n          - /url: /Triserc\n        - text: Ad\n        - button \"More\" [ref=e53] [nth=1]\n        - text: I typed in a domain and got this\n        - button \"Play Video\" [ref=e54]\n        - link \"From triserc.com\" [ref=e55]:\n          - /url: https://triserc.com/try?twclid=27ehfd9elxxxqsg689b215dv0h\n        - group \"3 reposts, 19 likes, 15 bookmarks, 164855 views\":\n          - button \"0 Replies. Reply\" [ref=e56]\n          - button \"3 reposts. Repost\" [ref=e57]: \"3\"\n          - button \"19 Likes. Like\" [ref=e58]: \"19\"\n          - link \"164855 views. View post analytics\" [ref=e59]:\n            - /url: /Triserc/status/2042342965063074090/analytics\n            - text: 164K\n          - button \"Bookmark\" [ref=e60] [nth=1]\n          - button \"Share post\" [ref=e61] [nth=1]\n      - article \"0xMarioNawfal Verified account @RoundtableSpace 21 hours ago THIS GUY JUST DROPPED AN 18-MIN TUTORIAL ON BUILDING ANIMATED WEBSITES Embedded video Play Video Attributed to Viktor Oddy 24 replies, 133 reposts, 1284 likes, 1916 bookmarks, 116319 views\" [ref=e62]:\n        - link \"Square profile picture\" [ref=e63]:\n          - /url: /RoundtableSpace\n        - link \"0xMarioNawfal Verified account\" [ref=e64]:\n          - /url: /RoundtableSpace\n          - text: 0xMarioNawfal\n        - link \"@RoundtableSpace\" [ref=e65]:\n          - /url: /RoundtableSpace\n        - link \"21 hours ago\" [ref=e66]:\n          - /url: /RoundtableSpace/status/2048647078642163898\n          - time: 21h\n        - button \"Grok actions\" [ref=e67] [nth=1]\n        - button \"More\" [ref=e68] [nth=2]\n        - text: THIS GUY JUST DROPPED AN 18-MIN TUTORIAL ON BUILDING ANIMATED WEBSITES\n        - button \"Play Video\" [ref=e69] [nth=1]\n        - text: From\n        - link \"Viktor Oddy Verified account\" [ref=e70]:\n          - /url: /i/status/2048363298652073994\n          - text: Viktor Oddy\n        - group \"24 replies, 133 reposts, 1284 likes, 1916 bookmarks, 116319 views\":\n          - button \"24 Replies. Reply\" [ref=e71]: \"24\"\n          - button \"133 reposts. Repost\" [ref=e72]: \"133\"\n          - button \"1284 Likes. Like\" [ref=e73]: 1.2K\n          - link \"116319 views. View post analytics\" [ref=e74]:\n            - /url: /RoundtableSpace/status/2048647078642163898/analytics\n            - text: 116K\n          - button \"Bookmark\" [ref=e75] [nth=2]\n          - button \"Share post\" [ref=e76] [nth=2]\n      - 'article \"Elon Musk Verified account @elonmusk 9 hours ago Scam Altman owned the OpenAI Startup fund while simultaneously lying to the world that he didn’t financially benefit from OpenAI Quote Captain Eli Verified account @TheCaptainEli 10 hour