{"type":"message","id":"69aadd89","parentId":"844da83b","timestamp":"2026-04-28T03:42:36.507Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_v7zzrwzx7oyp_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# For You Feed Posts - 2026-04-27\n\n## Post 1\n**@JulianGoldieSEO** | 22h ago\nBuild local AI agent with Ollama + Gemma 4 + PI Agent + Parallel Web Search MCP. Free alternative to $20-500/mo agents.\n📊 3.7K views | 81 likes | 132 bookmarks\n\n## Post 2\n**@eclincher** (Ad) | AI Social Media Agent tool - create, schedule, approve posts. $25/mo.\n📊 2.7M views | 181 likes\n\n## Post 3\n**@boxmining** | 18h ago\nOpenClaw 4.24 drops: Google Meet integration, DeepSeek V4 models, Gemini live voice, browser fixes.\n📊 9.2K views | 86 likes\n\n## Post 4\n**@DHSgov** | 3h ago | via @Kimberlyrja8\n\"ICE is NICE.\"\n📊 305K views | 15K likes\n\n## Post 5\n**@AntoineRSX** | 23h ago\nChinese lab open-sourced AI that builds video games from one prompt. Hardest test for coding agents.\n📊 3.5K views | 35 likes\n\n## Post 6\n**@googlegemma** | 10h ago\nCompletely local browser agent powered by Gemma 4 + WebGPU. Searches browsing history, summarizes pages, manages tabs. 100% local, no servers.\n📊 280K views | 4K likes\n\n## Post 7\n**@elonmusk** | 11h ago\n\"Scam Altman and Greg Stockman stole a charity. Full stop.\" - Claims Altman got tens of billions in side deals. 18M views, 120K likes.\n📊 18M views | 120K likes\n\n---\n*Scrolling more...*\n\n## Post 8\n**@plutusmedia** (Ad) | UGC agency marketing - \"one of the most respected operators called us the best UGC agency out there\"\n📊 1.8M views | 239 likes\n\n## Post 9\n**@gregisenberg** | 3h ago\n64-min OpenAI Codex masterclass. Covers: Claude vs Codex, running Claude Code inside Codex, GPT 5.5 for browser agents.\n📊 30K views | 332 likes | 610 bookmarks\n\n## Post 10\n**@sairahul1** | 21h ago\nMicrosoft open-sourced VibeVoice ASR - free 7B model that transcribes 60 mins of audio in one pass. 50+ languages, full diarization, no chunking. Killed ElevenLabs, AssemblyAI, Deepgram pricing.\n📊 830K views | 3K likes | 4.8K bookmarks\n\n## Post 11\n**@NousResearch** | 3h ago\nHermes agent can now run TouchDesigner (powerful real-time visual tool). Video by @macbethAI using the TouchDesigner skill.\n📊 44K views | 876 likes | 638 bookmarks\n\n## Post 12\n**@maverickecom** | 5h ago\nClaude + Arcads = 550 slideshow posts per day. Pro tip: have models hold iPhone over face for more realistic AI look.\n📊 17K views | 170 likes\n\n## Post 13\n**@Teknium** | 23h ago\nHermes Agent tip: backup and transfer your agent with `hermes backup` → creates a zip. Install fresh on new machine, transfer zip. Works across VPS, Mac Mini, anywhere.\n📊 57K views | 1.4K likes | 909 bookmarks\n\n## Post 14\n**@everestchris6** | 7h ago\nOpenClaw bot finds restaurants with ugly menus, rebuilds them as live web menus, mails owner a postcard... on autopilot. Scrapes every restaurant in a city, filters by review count.\n📊 148K views | 1.1K likes | 1.9K bookmarks\n\n## Post 15\n**@13Calendar** (Ad) | \"Your birthday might be wrong.\" 13-month calendar with 28 days per month. Find your real birthday.\n📊 2.8M views | 2.6K likes\n\n## Post 16\n**@this_is_tasnim** | 23h ago\n\"Goodbye Claude Code subscription fees.\" Someone built a proxy that runs Claude Code completely free using a free NVIDIA API key. Converts Anthropic API calls to NVIDIA.\n📊 99K views | 1.2K likes | 1.7K bookmarks\n\n## Post 17\n**@VadimStrizheus** | 10h ago\nOpenAI watching its ex-employees build a $1 trillion AI company in just 5 years. Anthropic hits record $1T valuation, 60% chance of IPO this year.\n📊 1.3M views | 19K likes\n\n## Post 18\n**@Ratioxdelratiox** | 10h ago\n\"And then there are those of us who post the first photo our friend takes of us, half-pixelated and with the whole face that God didn't want to give to anyone else\" (parody, Spanish translation)\n📊 635K views | 2.8K likes\n\n## Post 19\n**@MbarkCherguia** | 21h ago\n\"What would cause this behavior?\" (curiosity/cringe video)\n📊 65K views | 588 likes\n\n## Post 20\n**@bloodylikeab0dy** | 22h ago\nJules in this episode of Euphoria.\n📊 2.8M views | 56K likes\n\n## Post 21\n**@TansuYegen** | 10h ago\n\"Ancient romans used lewis tools\" (history/工具 trivia, 8.7M views!)\n📊 8.7M views | 28K likes\n\n## Post 22\n**@BuildAmericanAI** (Ad) | \"AI doesn't know borders. But the innovators that make it do.\" - Lobbying for a national AI solution instead of state-by-state regulations.\n📊 2.1M views | 243 likes\n\n## Post 23\n**@WallStreetApes** | 2h ago\nNewer Hyundai Genesis vehicles come with a 'crystal ball' rotary gear shift dial. Renters have no idea how to change gears because it just looks like a lit crystal ball.\n📊 157K views | 287 likes\n\n## Post 24\n**@noturtlesoup17** | 6h ago\nUpdate on the Lincoln Memorial Reflecting Pool — they are painting over the bright blue that Doug Burgum originally shared. Unclear if it's primer or a changed plan.\n📊 1M views | 2.9K likes\n\n## Post 25\n**@Asi1278310** | 22h ago\n\"There is an art in these complications too.\"\n📊 613K views | 822 likes\n\n## Post 26\n**@thirdmetax** | Apr 26\nMrBeast reveals a founder of a $2 billion company made all 100 employees read his leaked employee manual.\n📊 52K views | 458 likes\n\n## Post 27\n**@MJTruthUltra** | 13h ago\n\"Ford's Nightmare Truck\" — AI cameras read face, eyes, emotions & \"fitness to drive.\" Won't shift out of park if not calm enough. Live feeds to insurance companies.\n📊 591K views | 7.8K likes\n\n## Post 28\n**@aimikoda** | 20h ago\nGPT Image 2 - Character Reference Sheet prompt. Create character reference sheets for Seedance 2.0 videos using reference image or text description.\n📊 70K views | 1.3K likes\n\n## Post 29\n**@RoundtableSpace** | 17h ago\nGPT Image 2 posters are now fully editable in Canva with separate layers for text and design.\n📊 69K views | 267 likes\n\n## Post 30\n**@SLYDpouch** (Ad) | Premium leather nicotine pouch holder. Magnetic closure, holds a full pack.\n📊 514K views | 44 likes\n\n## Post 31\n**@MAGAVoice** | 7h ago\nTrump posted video of him playing tennis with Serena Williams. \"EVERYBODY loves Trump.\"\n📊 1.1M views | 31K likes\n\n## Post 32\n**@videothread3** | 16h ago\n\"Still processing what I am watching?\" (viral video hook)\n📊 1M views | 1.7K likes\n\n## Post 33\n**@Triserc** (Ad) | \"I typed in a domain and got this.\"\n📊 164K views | 19 likes\n\n## Post 34\n**@RoundtableSpace** | 21h ago\n18-minute tutorial on building animated websites (via Viktor Oddy).\n📊 116K views | 1.2K likes\n\n## Post 35\n**@elonmusk** | 9h ago\n\"Scam Altman owned the OpenAI Startup fund while simultaneously lying to the world that he didn't financially benefit.\" + quote from @TheCaptainEli defending Elon vs Altman.\n📊 5.2M views | 37K likes\n\n## Post 36\n**@eddieeizner** | Apr 26\n\"Here's exactly how $112,303 in 90 days with AI YouTube Automation.\"\n📊 36K views | 588 likes\n\n---\n*Continued scrolling...*"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777347756507}}
